      • addAllActors

        public void addAllActors​(java.lang.String actorsFile)
        Reads the input file ("nextBechdel_castGender.txt"), and adds all its Actors to this movie. Each line in the movie has the following formatting: Input String has the following formatting: "MOVIE TITLE","ACTOR","CHARACTER_NAME","TYPE","BILLING","GENDER" Example of input: "Trolls","Ricky Dillon","Aspen Heitz","Supporting","18","Male"
